  <h2>Why this shape works</h2>
  <ol class="play">
    <li><b>Personal line first.</b> Warm contacts smell a template instantly. The one true sentence up top earns the next ten.</li>
    <li><b>Specific proof, not adjectives.</b> "$12,400 across three fixes" beats "save money" every time. A real number is impossible to argue with.</li>
    <li><b>The guarantee removes the risk, so you never discount.</b> "2x or you don'''t pay" reframes $999 from a cost into a free look with upside.</li>
    <li><b>The ask is tiny.</b> "Send the one-pager or grab 15 minutes" is a yes anyone can give. You are not asking them to buy, only to look.</li>
  </ol>
  <div class="tip"><b>One move that lifts reply rates:</b> record a 20-second selfie video for your 3 warmest instead of typing the DM. Same words, your face. Warm contact plus a talking human is the highest-converting outreach there is, and almost nobody does it.</div>

