  <div class="funnel">
    <div class="fstep"><b>10</b><span>outreaches today</span></div>
    <div class="fstep"><b>~1</b><span>conversation</span></div>
    <div class="fstep"><b>0.5</b><span>call</span></div>
    <div class="fstep"><b>0.25</b><span>audit</span></div>
  </div>
  <p class="legend">Your sprint funnel is 200 outreach → 20 conversations → 10 calls → 5 audits. Warm contacts convert far higher than cold, so these 10 are your best single shot at the whole month. Do them properly, not fast.</p>

